						<div class="postbody"><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">x_collision = ( object1_xmin &lt; object2_xmax ) &amp;&amp; ( object1_xmax &gt; object2_xmin)<br />y_collision = ( object1_ymin &lt; object2_ymax) &amp;&amp; ( object2_ymax &gt; object2_ymin)<br /><br />collision = x_collision &amp;&amp; y_collision</div></div>

