				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Rect collision should test is the rects are <strong>not</strong> intersect, rather than is they intersect. It is faster. Like, if (x1+width1)&lt;x2, you already know that there is no collision, and can skip all further checks.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

